0\u002FPentagon-9-11-memorial-ap-2.jpg?ve=1&tl=1",externalUrl:a,copyright:a,source:a,isSpotlight:c,responsiveImages:[{media:J,srcset:"https:\u002F\u002Fa57.foxnews.com\u002Fstatic.foxnews.com\u002Ffoxnews.com\u002Fcontent\u002Fuploads\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F1470\u002F828\u002FPentagon-9-11-memorial-ap-2.jpg?ve=1&tl=1 2x"},{media:K,srcset:"https:\u002F\u002Fa57.foxnews.com\u002Fstatic.foxnews.com\u002Ffoxnews.com\u002Fcontent\u002Fuploads\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F1862\u002F1048\u002FPentagon-9-11-memorial-ap-2.jpg?ve=1&tl=1 2x"}]}},{is:b,props:{text:"\u003Chtml\u003E\u003Chead\u003E\u003C\u002Fhead\u003E\u003Cbody\u003EThere are still too many in this world who hate America and want to destroy our way of life and attack the freedoms our country offers, Olson said. He hopes this memorial can serve as a reminder to be vigilant.&nbsp;\u003C\u002Fbody\u003E\u003C\u002Fhtml\u003E"}},{is:b,props:{text:"\u003Chtml\u003E\u003Chead\u003E\u003C\u002Fhead\u003E\u003Cbody\u003E\"We must not let our guard down,\" he said.\u003C\u002Fbody\u003E\u003C\u002Fhtml\u003E"}},{is:b,props:{text:"\u003Chtml\u003E\u003Chead\u003E\u003C\u002Fhead\u003E\u003Cbody\u003EWith his birthday now forever linked to a grievous act of terrorism and a personal heartache, Olson said he doesn't try to celebrate his annual trip around the sun on some other artificial date. His birth milestone will always be the day of Barbara's death.&nbsp;\u003C\u002Fbody\u003E\u003C\u002Fhtml\u003E"}},{is:b,props:{text:"\u003Chtml\u003E\u003Chead\u003E\u003C\u002Fhead\u003E\u003Cbody\u003E\"Whatever pain and memories go along with this, that's part of living,\" Olson said. \"You can’t just make it disappear.\"\u003C\u002Fbody\u003E\u003C\u002Fhtml\u003E"}}],title:e,canonical_url:aA,article_slug:an,vanity_slugs:[],presentation_type:am,fn__syndication_info:[],fn__stock_ticker_symbols:a,post_version:1051648,component_type:"news_article",content_type:"spark_post",fn__site_search:d,stocks:[],meta:{chartbeat:{title:e,viewID:aq,s